00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:57.960
And that's when Vladimir Putin annexed Crimea,

00:07:57.960 --> 00:08:00.450
part of southern Ukraine, and fed the fighting

00:08:00.450 --> 00:08:02.610
in the east of the country.

00:08:02.610 --> 00:08:05.620
And he didn't pay a large price for that.

00:08:05.620 --> 00:08:09.780
So the concern now is Vladimir Putin may not stop there.

00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:12.090
