And there's new data tonight on child poverty in this country.

00:13:02.510 --> 00:13:06.620
The number of children living in poverty rose from 3.7 million

00:13:06.620 --> 00:13:10.170
since the child tax credit expired at the end of December.

00:13:10.170 --> 00:13:13.820
That's an increase of 41% according to a study

00:13:13.820 --> 00:13:15.650
by Columbia University.

00:13:15.650 --> 00:13:19.370
A quarter of Black and Latino children now live in poverty.

00:13:19.370 --> 00:13:23.070
That's more than double that of white children.

00:13:23.070 --> 00:13:24.500
Well, turning now to the Olympics

00:13:24.500 --> 00:13:27.650
where the fallout continues, following the stunning end

00:13:27.650 --> 00:13:29.660
to the women's figure skating final.

00:13:29.660 --> 00:13:34.580
from Beijing, here's CBS's Jamie Yuccas.

00:13:34.580 --> 00:13:38.660
Kamila Valieva was welcomed home to Russia today, just hours

00:13:38.660 --> 00:13:41.680
after her disastrous performance in the skating finals.

00:13:41.680 --> 00:13:44.630
That's the most mistakes that we've ever seen Kamila make.

00:13:44.630 --> 00:13:47.960
Valieva's fall from grace prompted the strongest response

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:51.000
yet from IOC President Thomas Bach.

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:54.260
I was very, very disturbed.

00:13:54.260 --> 00:13:56.570
Bach says he was especially concerned

00:13:56.570 --> 00:14:01.670
when he saw her coach scold her saying, why did you let it go?

00:14:01.670 --> 00:14:03.380
Why did you stop fighting?

00:14:03.380 --> 00:14:08.420
When I afterwards saw how she was received by her closest

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:14.460
entourage with what appeared to be a tremendous coldness,

00:14:14.460 --> 00:14:15.870
it was chilling.

00:14:15.870 --> 00:14:18.750
Valieva tested positive for a banned heart medication

00:14:18.750 --> 00:14:19.620
in December.

00:14:19.620 --> 00:14:23.370
But she was cleared to compete in part because she's a minor.

00:14:23.370 --> 00:14:25.770
How important is it to start looking at those people

00:14:25.770 --> 00:14:27.570
within her inner circle?

00:14:27.570 --> 00:14:30.360
It's of extreme importance.

00:14:30.360 --> 00:14:36.240
Doping very rarely happens alone by the athletes.

00:14:36.240 --> 00:14:38.280
Valieva's case has renewed attention

00:14:38.280 --> 00:14:41.280
on Russia's Olympic ban for state-sponsored doping,

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:43.230
which is set to expire this year.

00:14:43.230 --> 00:14:46.140
And it's rekindled debate among several governing

00:14:46.140 --> 00:14:49.410
bodies over raising the minimum age to compete.

00:14:49.410 --> 00:14:53.860
We will initiate such a discussion

00:14:53.860 --> 00:14:58.740
and at least give them some food for thought.

00:14:58.740 --> 00:15:00.420
As a side note, Elana Meyers Taylor

00:15:00.420 --> 00:15:03.240
will be the American flag bearer in this weekend's closing

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:04.050
ceremony.

00:15:04.050 --> 00:15:05.580
She had to skip that honor, you may

00:15:05.580 --> 00:15:07.440
remember, in the opening ceremony

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:09.870
after she tested positive for COVID.

00:15:09.870 --> 00:15:14.130
It will take place after she goes for gold in this weekend's

00:15:14.130 --> 00:15:15.450
two-woman bobsled.

00:15:15.450 --> 00:15:15.960
Jericka.

00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:16.860
Let's hope she wins.

00:15:16.860 --> 00:15:18.640
Jamie Yuccas, thank you.

00:15:18.640 --> 00:15:21.090
Still ahead on tonight's CBS Evening News,

00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:23.520
powerful winds cause harrowing landings

00:15:23.520 --> 00:15:25.680
at a major international airport.

00:15:25.680 --> 00:15:28.140
And avocados make a comeback.

00:15:28.140 --> 00:15:31.840
How diplomats helped to lift the ban on Mexican avocados.

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:36.740


00:15:36.740 --> 00:15:39.410
Tonight, newly released video shows the moment

00:15:39.410 --> 00:15:42.350
heavy rains triggered a deadly mudslide this week

00:15:42.350 --> 00:15:44.690
in the Brazilian city of Petropolis.

00:15:44.690 --> 00:15:47.690
The death toll is well over 100, and dozens more

00:15:47.690 --> 00:15:49.460
are still unaccounted for.

00:15:49.460 --> 00:15:52.880
Almost a foot of rain came down in about three hours.

00:15:52.880 --> 00:15:56.390
While winds topping 120 miles per hour

00:15:56.390 --> 00:15:58.970
howled across Britain today, it turned landing

00:15:58.970 --> 00:16:02.540
at London's Heathrow Airport into a nail-biting spectator

00:16:02.540 --> 00:16:03.200
sport.

00:16:03.200 --> 00:16:06.080
Hundreds of thousands of people watched a live stream

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:08.690
of planes struggling to stay on course

00:16:08.690 --> 00:16:10.490
through those dangerous gusts.

00:16:10.490 --> 00:16:13.520
Dozens of flights had to be canceled.

00:16:13.520 --> 00:16:15.740
And the US embassy today lifted the ban

00:16:15.740 --> 00:16:18.020
on inspections of Mexican avocados,

00:16:18.020 --> 00:16:20.360
clearing the way for exports to resume.

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:23.930
Deliveries of avocados were temporarily halted last week.

00:16:23.930 --> 00:16:27.290
An American inspector was threatened in an area of Mexico

00:16:27.290 --> 00:16:30.500
where growers are often shaken down by drug cartels.

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:32.960
The US and Mexico have now agreed

00:16:32.960 --> 00:16:36.230
to ensure the safety of inspectors.

00:16:36.230 --> 00:16:39.230
Well, On the Road is next with a Florida school

00:16:39.230 --> 00:16:41.660
and its very cool visitor.

00:16:41.660 --> 00:16:44.390


00:16:44.390 --> 00:16:47.640
If you can't watch the CBS Evening News, you can listen.

00:16:47.640 --> 00:16:49.770
